This directory is meant to store static files that need to be processed such
as original images to convert to sprites, SCSS files that will be converted
to CSS, etc.

# To generate main CSS file:
sass --watch  components/scss/hubble.scss:src/spacetelescope/static/css/hubble.css

# To generate events_embed CSS file:
sass --watch  components/scss/events_embed.scss:src/spacetelescope/static/css/events_embed.css

# To generate CSS sprites:
bin/glue components/sprites src/spacetelescope/static/sprites --url=../sprites/ --recursive --padding=1 --namespace=
